WEBVTT

00:01:13.030 --> 00:01:15.197
vi heyst ir?

00:01:15.197 --> 00:01:16.847
ZIGMUND NEUFELD.

00:01:16.847 --> 00:01:18.988
ven zayt ir geboyrn gevorn?

00:01:18.988 --> 00:01:22.029
in akhtn OF APRIL nayntsn zekhtsn.

00:01:22.029 --> 00:01:22.999
vu?

00:01:22.999 --> 00:01:24.794
in WARSCHAU.

00:01:24.794 --> 00:01:26.588
vi hot geheysn ayer tate?

00:01:26.588 --> 00:01:28.617
Avrom NEUFELD.

00:01:28.617 --> 00:01:32.088
tsi veyst ir vu er iz geboyrn gevorn?

00:01:32.088 --> 00:01:33.108
in Varshe.

00:01:33.108 --> 00:01:34.011
oykh in Varshe.

00:01:33.779 --> 00:01:34.344
oykh in Varshe.

00:01:34.346 --> 00:01:37.117
in velkhn yor?

00:01:36.918 --> 00:01:40.117
velkhn yor veys ikh nisht genoy, ken ikh nisht gedenken.

00:01:40.117 --> 00:01:43.323
ven iz dos letste mol vos ir hot im gezen?

00:01:43.181 --> 00:01:45.176
nayntsn nayn un draysik.

00:01:45.176 --> 00:01:47.088
in nayn un draysikstn yor.

00:01:47.088 --> 00:01:51.058
un vi alt iz er geven demolst umgefar?

00:01:51.058 --> 00:01:52.676
zibn in fuftsik yor.

00:01:52.676 --> 00:01:53.911
zibn un fuftsik.

00:01:53.911 --> 00:01:56.852
iz heyst dos az er iz mistome geboyrn arum akhtsn-

00:01:56.852 --> 00:02:00.793
akhtsn akhtsik, epes azoy.

00:02:00.793 --> 00:02:04.205
vos iz geven ayer tate's fakh?

00:02:04.205 --> 00:02:06.735
hot er, er hot gehandlt mit JUNK.

00:02:06.735 --> 00:02:07.646
vos heyst?

00:02:07.646 --> 00:02:10.440
shmates, flesher, di zakhn.

00:02:10.440 --> 00:02:13.411
hot er gehat a gevelb?

00:02:13.411 --> 00:02:15.958
hot gehat zayn SHOP, aza SHOP azan oyfgeshtelt.

00:02:15.617 --> 00:02:20.556
s'iz geven a teyl fun, fun dem hoyz vu ir hot gevoynt, oder bazunder?

00:02:19.142 --> 00:02:22.382
neyn, neyn, bazunder.

00:02:22.382 --> 00:02:24.235
s'iz geven groys?

00:02:24.235 --> 00:02:28.969
s'iz geven groys, s'iz geven a, azoy vi a GARAGE.

00:02:28.969 --> 00:02:32.499
iz mentshn flegn im brengen skhoyre?

00:02:32.499 --> 00:02:40.263
yo, di ale vos zenen gehandlt in, oyf di ⟨heyf⟩, gekoyft UNK dortn, gebrengt dort ahin tsum tatn tsu farkoyfn.

00:02:40.263 --> 00:02:43.440
hot er gemakht a gut lebn derfun?

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:49.440
a gut lebn, er hot gelebt. koym oysgekumen mitn lebn.

00:02:49.440 --> 00:02:51.735
vi hot geheysn di mame?

00:02:51.735 --> 00:02:54.294
Tsirl NEUFELD.

00:02:54.294 --> 00:02:57.535
un zi iz geven elter, tsi yu- tsi yunger?

00:02:56.556 --> 00:03:00.323
yunger mit a tsvey dray yor.

00:03:00.323 --> 00:03:01.941
vu iz zi geboyrn?

00:03:01.941 --> 00:03:04.735
oykh in Varshe.

00:03:04.735 --> 00:03:10.588
gedenkt ir di bobes mit di zeydes?

00:03:10.588 --> 00:03:14.970
ikh gedenk shoyn nisht vayl ikh hob zey nisht shoyn gezen mer.

00:03:14.970 --> 00:03:17.176
vi hobn zey geheysn?

00:03:17.176 --> 00:03:19.647
der zeyde hot geheysn Zelik.

00:03:19.647 --> 00:03:23.310
velkhn, velkhe zeyde? fun dem tatn's?

00:03:21.529 --> 00:03:26.940
fun tatn's zeydn, Zelik. un di mame's

00:03:26.940 --> 00:03:32.146
hot geheysn SEIDMAN, di, UNK fun der heym.

00:03:32.146 --> 00:03:34.705
un der ershter nomen?

00:03:34.705 --> 00:03:38.675
ROSENBAUM.

00:03:38.675 --> 00:03:42.467
un hot der tate gehat shvester mit brider?

00:03:42.467 --> 00:03:43.425
yo.

00:03:43.510 --> 00:03:44.510
vifl?

00:03:45.440 --> 00:03:49.587
hot er gehat a dray shvestern un tsvey brider in Varshe.

00:03:49.587 --> 00:03:52.705
vi hobn zey geheysn?

00:03:52.705 --> 00:03:58.852
eyner hot geheysn Ele, un

00:03:58.852 --> 00:04:03.734
un eyner hot geheysn Ele, un eyner hot geheysn Shaye,

00:04:03.734 --> 00:04:08.293
un di shvestern gedenk ikh nisht azoy genoy, eyn shvester gedenk ikh.

00:04:08.293 --> 00:04:12.028
hot geheysn Ester, oykhet.

00:04:12.028 --> 00:04:15.558
zey hobn ale gevoynt in Varshe? ir gedenkt zey?

00:04:13.421 --> 00:04:14.675
in Varshe. oykh.

00:04:15.558 --> 00:04:22.352
neyn. eyn, eyn bruder gedenk ikh vos er iz gekumen oyf Tshenstekhov, farshteyt zikh forn tsum tatn

00:04:22.352 --> 00:04:26.058
un oyf der mame's zayt, shvester mit brider?

00:04:26.058 --> 00:04:32.705
geven a bruder, hot er geheysn Leybl, oykh in Varshe geboyrn.

00:04:32.705 --> 00:04:37.017
ir zent geboyrn in Varshe. hot ir gelebt in Varshe di ale yorn?

00:04:37.037 --> 00:04:43.881
neyn. ikh hob gelebt eyn yor nor in Varshe, un di ale yor hob ikh gelebt in Tshenstekhov.

00:04:43.881 --> 00:04:47.381
far vos zayt ir aroys fun fun Varshe?

00:04:47.381 --> 00:04:51.715
di eltern zenen aroysgeMOVED, aroysgeforn, nor oyf di gantse...

00:04:50.440 --> 00:04:53.029
ober far vos?

00:04:53.029 --> 00:04:56.852
me hot gehat mishpokhe in Tshenstekhov oykhet, un

00:04:56.852 --> 00:05:01.071
der tate hot zikh gemakht a gevelbl in Tshenstekhov, UNK efsher beser

00:05:01.071 --> 00:05:04.475
makhn a gesheft, iz beser makhn do.

00:05:04.475 --> 00:05:07.675
hot ir shvester un brider?

00:05:07.675 --> 00:05:10.323
eyn shvester.

00:05:10.323 --> 00:05:12.499
un ir hot gehat andere?

00:05:12.499 --> 00:05:19.205
yo, ikh hob gehat tsvey brider hob ikh gegat, un eyn shvester nokh.

00:05:19.205 --> 00:05:21.999
ver iz der eltster fun di ale kinder?

00:05:21.999 --> 00:05:25.087
di shvester Blume.

00:05:25.087 --> 00:05:27.911
mit vifl yor elter iz zi geven fun aykh?

00:05:27.911 --> 00:05:29.616
akht yor elter.

00:05:29.616 --> 00:05:33.058
iz zi geboyrn heyst es in arum nayntsn elf?

00:05:33.058 --> 00:05:34.911
nayntsn elef.

00:05:34.911 --> 00:05:36.616
hot zi khasene gehat?

00:05:36.616 --> 00:05:40.381
yo, zi hot, zi hot, zi hot khasene gehat dos tsveyte mol.

00:05:40.381 --> 00:05:43.558
di ershte mol iz der man gevezn

00:05:43.558 --> 00:05:47.440
a beker, geh- er hot geheysn PRZEROSKI.

00:05:47.440 --> 00:05:51.263
un, un er iz aroysgekumen oyf zumer voynung,

00:05:51.263 --> 00:05:55.381
er iz zikh geganen bodn, un er iz gevorn UTOPIEt, der man.

00:05:55.381 --> 00:05:56.522
dertrunken gevorn?

00:05:56.422 --> 00:06:01.029
dertrunken gevorn, hot men im gebrengt nokh Tshenstekhov fun dorf.	

00:06:01.029 --> 00:06:06.764
un dos iz gevezn, nokh dem hot zi ge-, a tsvey dray yor hot zi khasene gehat shpeter.

00:06:06.764 --> 00:06:08.569
mit Frenken.

00:06:07.898 --> 00:06:16.588
mit Frenkl. az mitn ershtn man, dos iz geven in velkhn yor vos vos zey hobn khasene gehat?

00:06:08.569 --> 00:06:09.292
yo.

00:06:16.588 --> 00:06:18.558
vi alt iz zi geven?

00:06:18.558 --> 00:06:23.646
zi iz, zi hot, ven zi hot khasene gehat

00:06:23.646 --> 00:06:28.283
iz zi alt gevezn dakht zikh mir fir un tsvontsik yor, fir un tsvontsik yor, yo, fir un tsvontsik

00:06:28.169 --> 00:06:28.906
dos ershte mol.

00:06:28.906 --> 00:06:29.359
yo.

00:06:29.359 --> 00:06:33.187
iz geven arum finf un draysik.

00:06:32.035 --> 00:06:32.734
yo.

00:06:33.235 --> 00:06:36.352
un der tsveyter man hot zi khasene gehat iz...

00:06:36.352 --> 00:06:42.735
fun dem ershtn man iz geblibn a kind, eyn kind, fun ershtn man. der tsveyter hot zi nisht gehat keyn kinder.

00:06:42.735 --> 00:06:48.617
der ershter man iz, er hot ⟨gevart oys⟩ der milkhome, zi hot oy- khasene gehat in nayntsn

00:06:48.617 --> 00:06:52.999
zibn un draysik, akht un draysik, dakht zikh mir azoy, mitn tsveytn man.

00:06:52.999 --> 00:06:55.058
iz vos iz gevorn mitn kind?

00:06:55.058 --> 00:06:58.499
der mamen, di mame hot es genumen mit

00:06:58.499 --> 00:07:08.176
oyf di, oyf di SELECTION, zi hot gezogt efsher vest ets blaybn lebn, gebts mir dos kind.

00:07:08.176 --> 00:07:12.529
gebts mir dos kind. un nokh dem iz zi geganen

00:07:12.529 --> 00:07:17.852
oyf di SELECTION, iz gegan der man, un me hot im gef- geshikt avek

00:07:17.852 --> 00:07:21.264
oykh avektsushikn mitn UNK, nokh.

00:07:21.264 --> 00:07:25.823
in in lager, in in Treblinke hot zi dort arayn

00:07:25.823 --> 00:07:32.705
iz mayn shvester geshtanen mit undz, zogt zi, "az er geyt, gey ikh oykhet," iz zi aribergelofn tsun im ariber.

00:07:32.705 --> 00:07:37.470
un zi ⟨hot geveynt tsu zey⟩, zogt zi, vu er vet, vu er vet zayn vil zi oykh zayn.

00:07:37.470 --> 00:07:40.714
un me hot zey, nisht gekont aynhaltn, iz zi aribergegan tsun im.

00:07:43.147 --> 00:07:45.911
ver iz geven nokh Blumen?

00:07:45.911 --> 00:07:48.205
nokh Blume iz geven a bruder, SALAK.

00:07:48.205 --> 00:07:53.617
SALAK. hot er khasene gehat?

00:07:53.617 --> 00:07:58.058
hot khasene gehat letstns, hot er gehat khasene gehat in Varshe.

00:07:58.058 --> 00:08:00.940
hot gearbet in Varshe, hot khasene gehat in Varshe.

00:08:00.940 --> 00:08:04.117
ven iz er, ven iz er geboyrn?

00:08:04.117 --> 00:08:06.646
er iz geboyrn

00:08:06.646 --> 00:08:09.617
 er iz geven yinger tsvey yor vi mayn shvester.

00:08:09.617 --> 00:08:15.146
iz nayntsn draytsn, nu. un er hot khasene gehat ven?

00:08:15.146 --> 00:08:17.823
efsher tsvey yor far di m- far di krig.

00:08:17.823 --> 00:08:22.440
vi hot geheysn zayn vayb?

00:08:22.440 --> 00:08:27.558
Khane hot zi geheysn. di baynomen gedenk ikh nisht genoy. Khane.

00:08:27.558 --> 00:08:31.158
un vos iz gevorn mit zey? mit SALAK un mit zayn vayb?

00:08:30.675 --> 00:08:35.087
SALAK iz geven, zi, zi hot men avek fun Varshe geblibn.

00:08:35.087 --> 00:08:39.763
un er iz gekumen aher nokh Tshenstekhov tsu di eltern, tsu undz.

00:08:39.763 --> 00:08:43.234
er iz geven in lager mit undz tsuzamen.

00:08:43.234 --> 00:08:48.469
nokh dem hot men gemakht a SELECTION, hot zikh gemakht a zakh vos eyner

00:08:48.469 --> 00:08:53.175
hot aroysgekhapt azan a REVOLVER, me hot geTRIED

00:08:53.175 --> 00:08:55.881
tsu shisn oyf emetsn,

00:08:55.881 --> 00:09:01.176
un m'iz gegan, me hot aroysgekhapt finef un tsvontsik mentshn fun di rey, fun di SELECTIONS

00:09:01.176 --> 00:09:07.499
un me hot zey oysgeshosn, ale finef un tsvontsik.

00:09:07.499 --> 00:09:08.881
iz nokh SALAKn?

00:09:08.881 --> 00:09:12.176
iz geven Berish, hob ikh gehat a bruder.

00:09:12.176 --> 00:09:16.058
hot men im geshikt nokh Oyshvits avek.

00:09:16.058 --> 00:09:19.029
iz er oykh gegan efsher tsvey dray monat,

00:09:19.029 --> 00:09:23.029
hot men gekrign a

00:09:23.029 --> 00:09:27.764
LETTER, er hot gekrign a hartsshlak, iz zey hobn undz geshikt a

00:09:27.764 --> 00:09:33.411
UNK, di CLOTHES HOME, UNK

00:09:33.411 --> 00:09:38.235
az Berish iz geboyrn arum nayntsn fuftsn?

00:09:38.235 --> 00:09:41.058
tsvey yor b- yinger fun mir gevezn.

00:09:41.058 --> 00:09:42.499
un dernokh zayt ir.

00:09:42.687 --> 00:09:43.270
ikh.

00:09:43.489 --> 00:09:44.260
un nokh aykh?

00:09:44.382 --> 00:09:48.322
iz mayn shvester do, vos zi lebt do. Ester, Ester.

00:09:48.322 --> 00:09:49.617
zi lebt do in Toronto?

00:09:49.617 --> 00:09:50.793
zi lebt in Toronto.

00:09:50.793 --> 00:09:53.117
un ven hot zi khasene gehat?

00:09:53.117 --> 00:09:57.352
zi hot khasene gehat in lager, in geto, di kleyne geto hot zi dort khasene gehat.

00:09:57.352 --> 00:09:59.322
un vi heyst zi yetst?

00:09:59.322 --> 00:10:01.028
 zi heyst Fiksl.

00:10:01.028 --> 00:10:01.881
Fiksl?

00:10:01.881 --> 00:10:03.781
dem man's nomen.

00:10:06.646 --> 00:10:11.616
vos gedenkt ir fun Tshenstekhov, vu ir hot gevoynt?

00:10:11.616 --> 00:10:13.411
fun dem, funem yugnt?

00:10:13.411 --> 00:10:19.381
fun di yugnt? s'iz gevezn organizatsyes, yidishe organizatsyes, gute.

00:10:19.381 --> 00:10:23.734
un s'iz gevezn antisemitish, iz gevezn zeyer groys antisemitish.

00:10:23.734 --> 00:10:25.234
far vos zogt ir azoy?

00:10:25.234 --> 00:10:28.822
vayl ikh bin geven a a p- a FOOTBALL PLAYER

00:10:28.822 --> 00:10:32.822
un ikh bin geganen, az me hot gevunen di GAME, di MATCH

00:10:32.822 --> 00:10:39.175
az ikh hob gevunen, hot men undz gevorfn shteyner, in di, in kop az yeder iz aheymgeganen tseblit fun di pletser arop.

00:10:39.175 --> 00:10:42.616
yedes mol di zelbe gevezn.

00:10:42.616 --> 00:10:46.499
un me hot zikh nisht getort vayzn dortn in zeyere, in di,

00:10:46.499 --> 00:10:51.234
s'iz geven UNK iz geven azan PLACE vos zey hobn gevoynt, bay di UNK dort

00:10:51.234 --> 00:10:57.087
un oyf di, s'iz geven di, mit di MATKA BOSKA JASNA GORA, hot nisht getort ahingeyn keyn yid.

00:10:57.087 --> 00:11:02.234
adurkhgeyn dort in gantsn. s'iz an antisemitishkeyt, nokh dem hobn zey gemakht a

00:11:02.234 --> 00:11:07.260
a, a shtikl pogrom hobn zey gemakht oyf yidn, dakht zikh nisht eyner gelozt

00:11:07.260 --> 00:11:09.617
dort fun zey, hobn zey gemakht a pogrom

00:11:09.617 --> 00:11:10.519
ir gedenkt dos?

00:11:10.339 --> 00:11:10.958
yo.

00:11:11.278 --> 00:11:12.638
in velkhn yor iz dos geven?

00:11:12.911 --> 00:11:16.419
s'iz gevezn

00:11:17.999 --> 00:11:26.292
s'iz geven eyder di DEUTSCHE zenen nokh arayngekumen. dos iz geven nayntsn zibn in draysik, tsi zeks un draysik, azoy, gedenk ikh genoy.

00:11:25.764 --> 00:11:28.646
vos gedenkt ir fun dem? vos iz geshen?

00:11:28.646 --> 00:11:35.440
s'iz geshen az, zey hobn, zey hobn zey, zey hobn geharget velkhn zey hobn getrofn, velkhn yid zey hobn getrofn hobn zey geharget.

00:11:35.440 --> 00:11:42.881
zey hobn nisht gelozt geyn, un dort iz geven a, a por man vos zenen geven shtark yunge tregers.

00:11:42.881 --> 00:11:46.940
farshteyst vos a treger iz? a treger heyst vos zey arbetn

00:11:46.940 --> 00:11:51.764
un sh-, un trogn mel, un m- dos, di shtarke,

00:11:51.764 --> 00:11:58.116
hobn zey zikh genumen un zey hobn gevust ver es iz, un zey hobn im tse- tseharget, tseshlogn eynem,

00:11:58.116 --> 00:12:04.617
hobn zey gemakht a pogrom nokh dem, zey hobn nisht aroysgelozt keyn eynem, zey hobn geharget vu zey hobn getrofn a yid.

00:12:04.617 --> 00:12:06.911
dort UNK.

00:12:06.911 --> 00:12:11.529
iz geven genug antisemitn. di greste antisemitishe UNK iz geven SPECIAL in Tshenstekhov.

00:12:13.087 --> 00:12:15.323
vu hot ir gevoynt in Tshenstekhov?

00:12:15.323 --> 00:12:20.146
ikh hob gevoynt GARCARSKA g- draysik.

00:12:20.146 --> 00:12:24.146
un vos, in a hoyz, in a gebayde?

00:12:24.146 --> 00:12:28.323
s'iz geven azan gebayde fun a finef

00:12:28.220 --> 00:12:28.945
shtokn?

00:12:28.323 --> 00:12:29.440
finef, finef,

00:12:29.440 --> 00:12:33.323
FAMILIES hobn gevoynt. tsvey shtok azoy, tsvey.

00:12:33.323 --> 00:12:38.911
FIVE FAMILIES hobn gevoynt. undz ho'mir dort gevoynt.

00:12:38.911 --> 00:12:42.852
az ir hot gehat a dire, fun vifl tsimer?

00:12:42.852 --> 00:12:48.441
eyn tsimer, ver hot gehat a dire? m'iz geshlofn tsu fus- tsu kopns un tsu fusns.

00:12:48.441 --> 00:12:53.400
un mit di mamen mitn tatn. dos hobn mir gehat, eyn R- eyn voynung, eyn ROOM hot men gehat.

00:12:57.529 --> 00:13:00.029
vu zent ir gegangen in shul?

00:13:00.029 --> 00:13:03.382
in shul? in Tshenstekhov.

00:13:03.382 --> 00:13:08.058
ober ikh meyn, vos far a, vos far a min shul? vos far a min shul?

00:13:08.058 --> 00:13:11.264
a religyez? a besmedresh, a?

00:13:11.264 --> 00:13:14.793
neyn, mit der tate bin ikh gegan ale tog in besmedresh in der fri.

00:13:14.793 --> 00:13:18.616
hob ikh gemuzt mitgeyn mit im, er iz geganen yedn tog tsum davenen in besmedresh.

00:13:18.616 --> 00:13:21.675
nor azoy fun, shabes, yontoyvim

00:13:21.675 --> 00:13:26.440
hobn mir gedavnt SPECIAL in a shul, vos der tate iz geven a MEMBER dort.

00:13:26.440 --> 00:13:34.999
hot er mikh genumen mit, yom kiper, ayngehilt mitn tales, ikh zol nisht nisht aroysgegan kholile nemen epes trinken, epes veys ikh vos iz geven.

00:13:35.499 --> 00:13:39.940
opgehitn iz er geven, der tate, zeyer yidish.

00:13:39.940 --> 00:13:43.352
voser shprakh hot ir geredt in der heym?

00:13:43.352 --> 00:13:46.911
yidish, oykh geredt un poylish.

00:13:46.911 --> 00:13:49.871
ober in der heym, in der heym hot ir geredt di b- di d-

00:13:49.469 --> 00:13:50.110
yidish.

00:13:50.110 --> 00:13:51.120
in di shtub?

00:13:50.146 --> 00:13:51.528
bloyz yidish.

00:13:51.528 --> 00:13:52.058
in shtub. in di shtub?

00:13:52.440 --> 00:13:54.044
alts yidish.

00:13:56.028 --> 00:13:58.940
zent ir geven a guter talmed?

00:13:58.940 --> 00:14:01.241
in kheyder, ikh bin geganen in kheyder.

00:14:02.588 --> 00:14:03.382
in vel-

00:14:03.382 --> 00:14:08.470
a halbn tog in kheyder un a halbn tog in di SCHOOL. s'iz geven az

00:14:08.470 --> 00:14:12.588
lernen zikh poylish in di SCHOOL a halbn tog, un a halbn tog in kheyder.

