in velkhe subyektn zayt ir geven shtark?

00:14:17.647 --> 00:14:20.647
subyekt- in in in lernen?

00:14:20.647 --> 00:14:23.264
yo, in di shtudyes.

00:14:23.264 --> 00:14:27.999
kh'hob gelernt, ikh bin nisht geven SPECIAL, kh'hob gelernt, kh'hob gekont gut ivre davenen.

00:14:27.999 --> 00:14:31.293
gute davenen hob ikh gekont, kon ikh, davenen.

00:14:31.293 --> 00:14:34.734
leygn tfiln, davenen, dos ales UNK.

00:14:34.734 --> 00:14:40.146
un un in poylish hob ikh mikh gelernt a bisl, hob ikh gelernt tsu poylish oykhet.

00:14:40.146 --> 00:14:45.529
vifl bafelkerung hobn gevoynt in, in Tshenstekhov?

00:14:45.529 --> 00:14:49.929
in Tshenstekhov iz geven a fuftsik toyznt bafelkerung.

00:14:49.474 --> 00:14:53.588
un fun, fun fun dem vifl iz geven yidn?

00:14:53.588 --> 00:14:59.235
yidn iz gevezn oykhet a, ikh veys, a fuftsn toyznt yidn iz gevezn efsher.

00:14:59.235 --> 00:15:00.941
az a minderheyt.

00:15:01.298 --> 00:15:05.832
avade geven a minderheyt, di yidn. Poyln, polyakn iz geven mer, tsvey mol toplt.

00:15:05.832 --> 00:15:08.432
vu hobn di yidn gevoynt?

00:15:08.432 --> 00:15:13.932
m- in MOSTn teyl hobn zey gevoynt umetum hobn zey, es iz geven tsu voynen,

00:15:13.932 --> 00:15:16.899
ober s'iz geven a gas, an alee

00:15:16.899 --> 00:15:21.299
ALEJA WOLNOSCI, alee, un groyse, di di raykhe iz geven UNK

00:15:21.299 --> 00:15:25.966
ver es hot gehat, ver s'iz geven raykh, ver es hot gehat gelt hot gekont hobn dort a voynung.

00:15:25.966 --> 00:15:32.400
ver es hot nisht gehat hot gevoynt oyf di GARCARSKA gas, NADRZECZNA gas, in di unter-gasn, d- YOU KNOW, UNK.

00:15:35.966 --> 00:15:38.132
ir gedenkt di shkheynim?

00:15:38.132 --> 00:15:43.899
fun der heym? ikh gedenk epes shkheynim.

00:15:43.899 --> 00:15:45.133
zaynen zey geven yidn?

00:15:45.133 --> 00:15:49.432
yidn, ale yidn vos ikh hob gehandlt. ikh hob gehat shpiln mit di yidn ales

00:15:49.432 --> 00:15:52.266
un ikh hob geshpilt in sport mit yidn ales, di gantse tsayt.

00:15:52.266 --> 00:15:54.637
hot ir gehat keyn goyishe fraynt?

00:15:54.637 --> 00:15:55.240
neyn.

00:15:55.240 --> 00:15:57.844
keyn mol nit? far vos nit?

00:15:57.844 --> 00:16:03.666
vayl ikh hob mikh nisht, ikh hob gezen az s'iz nisht mayne FRIEND. ikh hob mikh nisht gekont opgebn.

00:16:03.666 --> 00:16:07.066
s'iz alts geven far⟨UNK⟩, ikh hob mikh nisht gekent opgebn mit zey.

00:16:07.066 --> 00:16:08.232
dort

00:16:08.232 --> 00:16:11.924
do hot er geredt, un do hot er gekont untn araynshtekhn a meser

00:16:14.265 --> 00:16:21.119
dortn vu ir zayt geven, gegangen in shul, iz dos geven vayt fun, funem hoyz, fun der gebayde?

00:16:18.980 --> 00:16:22.280
fi- funem, neyn, neyn.

00:16:22.499 --> 00:16:28.832
s'iz geven a groyse shul, a sheyne, yidishe shul. iber di shul iz geven a klenere besmedresh

00:16:28.832 --> 00:16:31.512
vos m'iz gegan in mitn der vokh yedern tog tsum davenen.

00:16:32.933 --> 00:16:37.966
vi azoy hot oysgezen Tshenstekhov? iz es geven altmodish, tsi modern?

00:16:37.966 --> 00:16:41.732
s'iz, s'hot oysgekukt gants sheyn, in Tshenstekhov.

00:16:41.732 --> 00:16:45.866
vi s'iz di di di unterge- di unter-gasn iz geven nisht modern, ober azoy.

00:16:45.866 --> 00:16:48.499
s'iz geven raykhe gasn, ALEJA WOLNOSCI

00:16:48.499 --> 00:16:55.299
fa- di drite alee, di tsveyte alee, di ershte alee, dos alts iz geven raykhe SECTIONS.

00:16:55.299 --> 00:17:00.749
hot ir gehat vaser ineveynik bay aykh in, in der gebay-?

00:16:59.299 --> 00:17:02.899
neyn, men hot gemuzt, men hot gemuzt brengen vaser fun untn.

00:17:02.899 --> 00:17:06.365
SO UNK hot men gemuzt geyn oyf a tsveyt PLACE un batsoln

00:17:06.365 --> 00:17:10.698
finef groshn far a WIADRO vaser. koyfn vaser.

00:17:10.698 --> 00:17:14.399
nor nokh dem hot men shoyn gemakht azan brune in

00:17:14.399 --> 00:17:16.999
a brune, un aroyfgetsoygn vaser.

00:17:16.999 --> 00:17:19.765
hot men shoyn gemuzt trogn aroys vaser in shtub arayn

00:17:19.765 --> 00:17:21.432
tsu vashn vesh,

00:17:21.432 --> 00:17:25.784
tsu makhn, di mame gekokht di vesh un gevashn di vesh, un UNK

00:17:27.632 --> 00:17:32.465
bashraybt mir a shabes, vi azoy ir hot gepravet shabes.

00:17:32.465 --> 00:17:38.632
shabes, shabes zenen mir ale gegan mit mitn tatn tsum davenen.

00:17:38.632 --> 00:17:42.866
dos hot men gemuzt tun yedern shabes, mit geyn tsum davenen.

00:17:42.866 --> 00:17:46.432
un undz ze'mir aheymgekumen fun davenen,

00:17:46.432 --> 00:17:50.333
zikh avekgezetst, der tate hot UNK gevolt az men zol zitsn baym tish ale.

00:17:50.333 --> 00:17:55.266
tsuzamen, ale tsuzamen baym tish, vos mit esn, tsum esn tsuzamen zitsn baym tish.

00:17:55.266 --> 00:18:01.233
nisht eyner zol kumen shpeter, un eyner frier, nor men zol zayn ale tsuzamen.

00:18:01.233 --> 00:18:04.099
vos flegt di mame kokhn?

00:18:04.099 --> 00:18:08.032
vos zi hot gehat hot zi gekokht.

00:18:08.032 --> 00:18:11.299
men iz nisht geven tsu raykh.

00:18:11.299 --> 00:18:16.733
vos me hot gekont zikh erloybn hot zi gekokht.

00:18:16.733 --> 00:18:20.433
hot ir gehat andere kroyvim in Tshenstekhov?

00:18:20.433 --> 00:18:22.999
in Tshenstekhov,

00:18:22.999 --> 00:18:26.766
hob ikh nisht gehat keyn kroyvim. kh'hob gehat bakante, hob ikh gegat.

00:18:26.766 --> 00:18:32.666
flegt ir, vi oft flegt ir tsunoyfkumen mit di kroyvim?

00:18:32.666 --> 00:18:36.779
vi? ikh hob nisht gehat keyn kroyvim, ikh hob nor gehat an ORGANIZATION bin ikh gevezn,

00:18:35.733 --> 00:18:40.933
neyn, ikh mayn mit ayer mishpokhe, in in Varshe tsum bayshpil.

00:18:40.933 --> 00:18:42.215
ah, in Varshe

00:18:41.063 --> 00:18:43.361
mit di feters, mit di tantes...

00:18:43.163 --> 00:18:44.982
in in Varshe bin ikh

00:18:43.991 --> 00:18:45.100
mit di kuzinen.

00:18:45.000 --> 00:18:48.066
iz mayn tate aleyn geforn, a mol ahin oder ahin,

00:18:48.066 --> 00:18:56.333
ober der bruder iz gekumen aher tsu undz do in Varshe, hot er gehat a a gesheft fun farbn, der bruder in Varshe.

00:18:56.333 --> 00:19:00.833
a groys gesheft fun farbn, alerley farbn.

00:19:00.833 --> 00:19:09.732
iz er do ahergekumen a mol, un der tate iz a mol ahingeforn, iz er geven gut avekgeshtelt, der der bruder.

00:19:09.732 --> 00:19:15.133
gehat a sheyn gesheft, er hot gemakht a gut lebn.

00:19:15.133 --> 00:19:18.533
un bay yomtoyvim flegt ir nisht tsunoyfkumen?

00:19:18.533 --> 00:19:21.766
ir redt nokh Varshe? neyn, s'iz vayt geven fun undz dokh Varshe.

00:19:21.766 --> 00:19:23.266
vi vayt iz es?

00:19:23.266 --> 00:19:30.133
s'iz tsu forn a, a finef sho, zeks sho.

00:19:30.133 --> 00:19:33.966
az tsum bayshpil peysekh tsayt, purim, khanike,

00:19:33.966 --> 00:19:39.733
ikh bin geforn aroys khanike mi- un, un kholemoyd hot men geflegt aroystsuforn,

00:19:39.733 --> 00:19:42.099
in a dorf, men hot tsamgenumen zikh fun dort

00:19:42.099 --> 00:19:46.406
organizatsye aribergeforn in dorf, aribergeforn do azoy.

00:19:51.966 --> 00:19:56.500
ir hot gehert tsu a klub, hot ir gezogt, tsu a krayz?

00:19:56.500 --> 00:19:59.533
kh'hob gehert, a sport klub, dos hob ikh gehert ob-

00:19:59.533 --> 00:20:04.340
a sport klub, hot es geheysn di ⟨GIAZNA⟩, dos iz geven di, di linke Poyeley-Tsien.

00:20:06.333 --> 00:20:11.099
az s'iz geven, ir, zent ir geven tetik mit politik?

00:20:11.099 --> 00:20:14.066
ikh bin, ikh bin nisht geven keyn orga- neyn, in sport.

00:20:14.066 --> 00:20:19.511
in politik hob ikh a bisl oykhet, ober in sport bin ikh gevezn meyn.

00:20:21.032 --> 00:20:23.933
mayn, mayn froy iz gevezn

00:20:23.933 --> 00:20:27.399
in di ORGANIZATION, un hot zi gehat

00:20:27.399 --> 00:20:30.970
a rosh-⟨hakn⟩ fun di ORGANIZATION, vos iz geven di eltste

00:20:32.166 --> 00:20:36.431
zey hobn getantst UNK, az di ale zakhn UNK mitgeganen, nisht undz

00:20:37.600 --> 00:20:41.766
vos iz a, vos far a mentsh iz geven der tate?

00:20:41.766 --> 00:20:45.999
der tate iz geven a, ikh zog dokh, er hot lib gehat, er hot gedavnt farn omed.

00:20:45.999 --> 00:20:47.666
hot geleyent seyfer,

00:20:47.666 --> 00:20:52.266
er hot, er hot gehandlt mit dem, er iz arayn mit di ale mentshn, s'iz dokh geven a sakh

00:20:52.266 --> 00:20:56.900
vos hobn gehat azelkhene GARAGES vos hobn gekoyft di flesher un di shmates,

00:20:56.900 --> 00:20:59.466
hot er gedavnt, un gemakht a shtibl

00:20:59.466 --> 00:21:03.100
az di ale zoln kumen tsum davenen do aher tsu im.

00:21:03.100 --> 00:21:06.066
un ale zoln brengen tsu farkoyfn tsu im.

00:21:06.066 --> 00:21:09.000
er hot gedavnt farn omed, er hot geleyent seyfer, er hot ales getun.

00:21:10.699 --> 00:21:15.566
iz er geven an ernster, tsi flegt er a mol vitslen, shpiln mit aykh?

00:21:15.566 --> 00:21:17.800
yo, yo,

00:21:17.800 --> 00:21:21.966
getseylte zakhn, - z- er hot zikh avekgeshtelt bay a seyder

00:21:21.966 --> 00:21:25.366
oprikhtn a seyder, hot es gedoyert biz tsvey draye bay nakht UNK

00:21:25.366 --> 00:21:29.866
di kitl ongetun, UNK azoy, oysgetaytsht yeder zakh undz, yeder zakh

00:21:32.366 --> 00:21:35.033
zent ir geven noent mit di geshvister?

00:21:35.033 --> 00:21:36.300
yo.

00:21:36.300 --> 00:21:38.000
mit di ale?

00:21:38.000 --> 00:21:42.033
hot ir gehat a balibstn bruder oder shvester?

00:21:42.033 --> 00:21:44.733
ale zenen geven glaykh, ale ale,

00:21:44.733 --> 00:21:49.766
zey hobn gelebt tsuzamen gut, ale di shvester un di brider.

00:21:49.766 --> 00:21:52.400
eyn bruder hob ikh gehat, hot er tsum meystn teyl,

00:21:52.400 --> 00:21:55.733
der SALAK, gearbet nor in Varshe hot er gearbet.

00:21:55.733 --> 00:22:01.332
un oyf di yontoyvim un dos iz er aheymgekumen in shtub aher.

00:22:01.332 --> 00:22:06.999
ikh hob oykh gearbet, hob ikh gearbet in Katovits, kh'hob nisht gevolt arbetn in Tshenstekhov vayl es zenen nisht gevezn

00:22:06.999 --> 00:22:11.433
keyn arbet, es iz nisht geven tsu fardinen, bin ikh, bin ikh geforn oyf Katovits, kh'hob gearbet in Katovits.

00:22:11.433 --> 00:22:12.433
ven iz dos geven?

00:22:12.433 --> 00:22:14.033
oyfn SEASON

00:22:14.033 --> 00:22:16.933
un nokhn SEASON bin ikh aheymgekumen un un dos.

00:22:16.933 --> 00:22:19.566
dos ales geven far di milkhome nokh.

00:22:19.566 --> 00:22:21.866
in vos hot ir gearbet?

00:22:21.866 --> 00:22:26.432
kh'hob gemakht damske mantlen, SUITS, di zakhn.

00:22:26.432 --> 00:22:29.833
ikh, me hot gearbet oyf shtik, PIECEWORK.

00:22:29.833 --> 00:22:31.560
s'heyst a shnayder zent ir geven?

00:22:31.233 --> 00:22:32.033
yo.

00:22:32.033 --> 00:22:34.833
vi azoy hot ir zikh oys- oysgelernt shnayderay?

00:22:34.833 --> 00:22:37.366
ikh hob mikh oysgelernt, ikh bin gegan in di alee

00:22:37.366 --> 00:22:40.733
tsu a shnayder lernen zikh shnayderay.

00:22:40.733 --> 00:22:42.389
vi alt zayt ir demolst geven?

00:22:42.379 --> 00:22:43.966
tsvelef yor.

00:22:43.966 --> 00:22:46.933
bin ikh shoyn gegan aroys.

00:22:46.933 --> 00:22:51.666
gezen vos tut zikh in der heym, bin ikh aroysgegan, zukhn efsher fardinen a por groshn.

00:22:51.666 --> 00:22:56.666
hot er mir gegebn di, di vos me shnaydt tsu, di shtiklekh vos me varft on oyf der erd, di

00:22:56.666 --> 00:23:00.100
opfal, hob ikh dos gegat oyf shabes

00:23:00.100 --> 00:23:04.099
oyf fraytik tsu nemen tsu farkoyfn, UNK a mol tsu geyn in a,

00:23:04.099 --> 00:23:07.000
in a keler arayn tsu geyn, azoy tsu lebn.

00:23:07.000 --> 00:23:10.166
iz der z- tate geven aynshtimik az ir zolt arbetn?

00:23:10.166 --> 00:23:12.366
yo.

00:23:12.366 --> 00:23:15.900
dos hot aykh nit geshtert mit di shtudyes?

00:23:15.900 --> 00:23:21.466
dos hob, ikh hob nisht gehat keyn eytse. se hot zikh gemakht nokh dem azoy shlekht, az s'iz nisht geven keyn parnose in der heym.

00:23:21.466 --> 00:23:24.409
men hot gemuzt geyn, yeder eyner aroyshelfn.

00:23:24.409 --> 00:23:32.166
nokh dem, bin ikh avekgeforn shoyn, ven ikh hob shoyn gekont arbetn, bin ikh geforn oyf Katovits arayn

00:23:32.166 --> 00:23:36.733
ikh hob mikh bazorgt, azoy ikh bin avekgeforn, hot di mame gevust az koyln

00:23:36.733 --> 00:23:41.500
un kartofl hob ikh ongegreyt, un shmalts hob ikh ongegreyt, ales vos ikh hob fardint

00:23:41.500 --> 00:23:47.466
dem SEASON, adurkhgearbet di dray monatn, fir monatn dort.

00:23:47.466 --> 00:23:52.232
ikh bin aheymgekumen, iz ales gevezn tsugegreyt in der shtub.

00:23:54.799 --> 00:24:00.832
dertseylt mir vayter vegn dos yidish lebn in, in ah Tshenstekhov.

00:24:00.832 --> 00:24:03.299
in Tshenstekhov iz gevezn

00:24:03.299 --> 00:24:10.233
zeyer a a a fayn lebn, di ORGANIZATIONS, di yidishe lebn iz tsuzamengekumen, ale organizatsyes

00:24:10.233 --> 00:24:16.633
un sport klubs, un in di shuln iz men zikh tsuzamen gekumen, un vu me, me hot gehat

00:24:16.633 --> 00:24:21.233
a veg iz men zikh tsuzamengekumen, gefirt farshidene zakhn.

00:24:21.233 --> 00:24:27.066
adurkh, KULTURA, a bisl geredt azoy farshidns.

00:24:27.066 --> 00:24:30.733
zayt ir geven aleyn a gloybiker?

00:24:30.733 --> 00:24:33.379
a gloybiker, yo, kh'hob gegloybt in got, yo.

00:24:32.066 --> 00:24:34.433
in reboyne shel oylem?

00:24:34.433 --> 00:24:38.466
ikh bin haynt oykh a gloybiker.

00:24:38.466 --> 00:24:41.166
flegt ir leygn tfiln ale tog?

00:24:40.227 --> 00:24:43.300
ale tog. haynt oykh, nu.

00:24:43.300 --> 00:24:45.933
der tate UNK, "du host ongemostn di tfiln?

00:24:45.933 --> 00:24:50.499
d- ze- gib a kuk tsi di kop iz dir nisht greser gevorn tsi klener gevorn."

00:24:50.499 --> 00:24:53.499
zog ikh, "tate, ikh hob ongemostn di tfiln, hob nisht keyn moyre."

00:24:58.866 --> 00:25:03.866
tsi gedenkt ir ven s'hot zikh ongehoybn tsu endern?

00:25:03.866 --> 00:25:07.600
ven es hot zikh ongehoybn tsu vern erger far di yidn?

00:25:07.600 --> 00:25:12.233
in Tshenstekhov? yo, zikher.

00:25:12.233 --> 00:25:13.466
ven?

00:25:13.466 --> 00:25:20.099
se, se, s'iz di gantse nisht gut geven far di yidn dort, ober erger hot zikh gemakht ven der DEUTSCH iz arayngekumen.

00:25:20.099 --> 00:25:24.366
hobn zey arayngeshtelt zikh in di WINDOWS arayn a tsleymen.

00:25:24.366 --> 00:25:28.933
farshteyst? mit a ke- likhtl ongetsundn, az do voynt a

00:25:28.933 --> 00:25:31.466
a krist, es voynt nisht keyn yid do.

00:25:31.466 --> 00:25:35.979
az zey zoln visn vos ⟨di yidn⟩, zey hobn ales ge- gemakht az dos.

00:25:37.732 --> 00:25:43.899
un ales hobn zey, me hot zi gegebn, aroysgegebn yidn, se iz geven yidn vos hobn zikh bahaltn in bunkers.

00:25:43.899 --> 00:25:47.799
zenen zey gegangen, aroysgegebn di yidn, vu zey zenen, far

00:25:47.799 --> 00:25:50.599
far a kilo tsuker hobn zey aroysgegebn di yidn.

00:25:50.599 --> 00:25:52.966
vi lang az zey hobn gehat tsu tsoln gelt

00:25:52.966 --> 00:25:57.899
iz shtil geven, es hot oyfgehert, s- zey hobn nisht gehat keyn gelt, hobn zey aroysgegebn di DEUTSCHEN.

00:25:57.899 --> 00:26:05.899
vos iz geshen in zibn dray- un draysik oder akht un draysik? epes?

00:26:05.899 --> 00:26:07.633
es iz nokh gor- in di zibn un draysik, nayn un dray-

00:26:07.633 --> 00:26:11.433
zibn un draysik, akht un draysik, di por yorn far der milkhome.

00:26:11.433 --> 00:26:15.433
hobn mir shoyn gehert az me hot, az me hot fun

00:26:15.433 --> 00:26:20.966
Berlin hot men shoyn yidn aroys, aroys- likvidirt, fun dan, me hot gehert, nor me hot zikh nisht,

00:26:20.966 --> 00:26:26.433
yidn hobn zikh nisht gelozt tsugleybn dos do, az es vet do dos vern.

00:26:26.433 --> 00:26:31.999
biz, biz nay-, az biz se hot zikh ongehoybn nayn un draysikstn yor, azoy vi zey zenen arayn

00:26:31.999 --> 00:26:35.100
hot men undz ale genumen aroys

00:26:35.100 --> 00:26:41.366
un arayngehakt in a tfise, un geshosn keseyder oyf di STEPS un UNK vi flign mentshn keseyder.

00:26:41.366 --> 00:26:46.166
un, zey hobn genumen, afile di CHURCHES hobn zey genumen un arayngeshtelt dort

00:26:46.166 --> 00:26:51.866
ferd mit alem, arayngeshtelt umetum, ven di DEUTSCHEN zenen arayngekumen, UNK azoy

00:26:51.866 --> 00:26:57.700
un un un undz ze'mir gezesn a sheyne por tog do in di tfise, gezesn.

00:26:57.700 --> 00:26:59.666
undz gehaltn dort.

00:26:59.666 --> 00:27:04.899
in in in GARAGES, un do umetum.

00:27:04.899 --> 00:27:08.766
s'iz keyn mol nisht gut geven in Poyln, se vet nisht gut zayn, nisht gut geven dortn.

00:27:08.766 --> 00:27:10.833
far yidn iz keyn mol nisht gut geven.

00:27:10.833 --> 00:27:15.700
ikh bin arumgegan in di gas, me hot gehandlt, a por mentshn, zey hobn gehat STORES oder vos iz

00:27:15.700 --> 00:27:20.499
zenen zey arumgeganen, zey hobn boykotirt, hobn zey gezu- gezungen oyf poylish

00:27:20.499 --> 00:27:27.200
NIE KUPUJ U ZIDA NAJLEPSZA RADA, KTO KUPUJE U ZYDA TEN SAM SIEBIE OKRADA

00:27:27.200 --> 00:27:31.633
ver es koyft a yi- bay a yid tut zikh aleyn baganvenen

00:27:31.633 --> 00:27:34.866
zolst nisht koyfn bay keyn yid, zolst nisht arayngeyn tsu keyn yid.

00:27:34.866 --> 00:27:40.633
un tsum sof hobn a sakh polyakn nisht gekukt, zey zenen arayngegan tsu yidn, vayl zey hobn farkoyft biliker vi bay zey.

00:27:40.633 --> 00:27:44.866
azoy iz arumgegan un gezungen bay di STORES, nisht tsugelozt keynem.

00:27:44.866 --> 00:27:52.565
zeyer antisemitish gevezn in der heym.

00:27:52.565 --> 00:27:57.498
vos iz geven in nayntsn nayn un draysik?

00:27:57.498 --> 00:28:01.498
nayntsn nayn un draysik iz arayn der DEUTSCH.

00:28:01.498 --> 00:28:06.232
un hot zikh gemakht a UNK, me hot geshosn, me hot geharget in di gasn umetum.

00:28:06.232 --> 00:28:10.965
un me hot gekhapt tsu der arbet, yedern tog, genumen tsu der arbet.

00:28:10.965 --> 00:28:14.899
oyf ⟨pleyzn⟩, yedern tog genumen tsu di ⟨pleyzn⟩.

00:28:14.899 --> 00:28:20.833
un se hot zikh, un yedern tog iz geven an andere mayse, me hot geharget, tsi geshosn, tsi me hot nisht gehat

00:28:20.833 --> 00:28:24.466
tsu esn m'iz geshtanen a LI- in a LINE, ikh bin geshtanen in a LINE

00:28:24.466 --> 00:28:26.366
hot men gegebn a shtikl broyt,

00:28:26.366 --> 00:28:29.666
ikh bin shoyn ongekumen bay dem fentster tsu krign dem shtikl broyt,

00:28:29.666 --> 00:28:32.466
ober iz tsugeganen a sheygets, hot er geshrign "s'iz a JUDE."

00:28:32.466 --> 00:28:35.766
hot men mikh aroysgevorfn tsurik. hob ikh ongekukt

00:28:35.766 --> 00:28:38.433
UNK yetst dem DEUTSCH, UNK nokh geven fri

00:28:38.433 --> 00:28:46.355
iz mayn mame aroysgegan, hot zi im gekusht di fis er zol mikh nisht hargenen, er zol mikh oplozn far dem vos ikh hob im ongekukt beyz.

00:28:46.355 --> 00:28:51.866
ikh bin shoyn geven bay dray, der driter mentsh dort baym fentster tsu krign a bisl broyt, hot men mikh aroysgeshlept.
